In the Destron base in Syria Halucigen noticed a bleep on the 
radars.  "Interesting" he said.  "All available Destrons we have a 
fast moving bot moving north.  Interecept ASAP." he said as he ran 
out of the base transforming with a flip in twist in an unearthly way 
into his vulturem ode as he flew off into the wind, letting his 
scences lead his way.

Neody got the message and he too left.
